snippet.title: OVERWHELMED - Trailer
snippet.description:
OVERWHELMED is a snappy Twin Stick Shooter with neon vibes!
Choose a spaceship and destroy 15 waves of powerful enemies before reaching the powerful boss!

🕹 More than 5 spaceship
🌃 A retro neon aesthetic
🔫 Lots of Pew-Pew
Steam Link :
